cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "genetic-algorithm: a pluggable-fitness evolutionary engine"
abstract: >-
  A small, dependency-free Python genetic-algorithm engine whose fitness
  criterion is a swappable plugin. Separating the evolutionary engine from the
  judgment of "better" makes the same loop reusable as the search core of an
  autoresearcher (generate -> evaluate -> select -> repeat), including
  LLM-as-a-judge criteria.
type: software
authors:
